title.en: Kokuryuu Heika no Seiryaku Hanayome - Majo desu ga, Tasuketa Ryuu ni Yomeiri Saserare sou desu
Akuma x Hanayome - Erabareta Musume wa Docchi?
Konyaku Haki Sareta Kaedama Reijou, Hatsukoi no Toshiue Ouji ni Dekiai Sareru
Guze no Seijo wa Akujiki Akuma ni Taberareru
Doku-suki Reijou wa Kekkon ni Tadoritsukai
Dokushin Shugi no Reijou wa, Koushaku-sama no Dekiai kara Nogaretai
Cheat Shoujo ga Boukun Seiou ni Dekiai saresou desu ga, Ima wa Mahou ni Muchuu nan desu!!!
"Akage no Yakutatazu" to Kubi ni natta Maryokunashi no Majo desu ga, "Yakusou no Chishiki ga Hanpanai!" to Ouritsu Kenkyuujo ni Soku Saiyou Saremashita.
Akugyaku Seijo desu ga, Aisuru Danna-sama no Oyaku ni Tachitai desu. (To wa Ie, Kirawarete Iru no desu ga)
Mofumofu Majuu to Heion ni Kurashitai no de Kowamote Koushaku no Kyuukon wa Okotowari desu
Yarinaoshi Tensei Reijou Hazamaa Shitai no ni Dekiaisareru
Kurokishi-sama kara Zenryoku de Dekiaisareteimasu ga, Sugomori Seijo wa Kyou mo Hikikomoritai!
Shukujo no Kagami Yamemashita. Toki wo Gyakkou shita Koushaku Reijou wa, Wagamama na Imouto ni Furimawasarenai you Seikaku Waruku Ikinobimasu!
